No amount of words, posts, or stories can truly express the depth of my love for you. Every day feels special because of you. I don’t need a birthday for the world to know how much you mean to me. You call me Swanushine, but the warmth I receive from you is truly extraordinary. Thank you for sharing all the laughter, the tears, and the joy. From being there for every milestone in our lives to video calling for hours on end, as if time doesn’t exist, you’ve been my constant. My life would genuinely be dull without you. It’s so true what they say – a carefree spirit and someone who carefully considers every decision can go incredibly far together. I love you, Nushku! Thank you for bringing so much energy and spark into my life. Here’s to our everlasting journey together! And to celebrating every milestone side-by-side.❤️

In between the process of developing diabetic-friendly bento cakes recipes & new tastebuds, I found myself to feel soooooo grateful to be blessed with the best support system 🥰

#sidequests #thankfulnomatterwhat
Exist as you are so I can love you for all that you are 🍃😇🤍

Somewhere in sync with my soul’s rhythm and my heart’s desire ✨
